-- Valeant may raise Allergan bid, says it won't walk away
-- 
-- Mon Oct 20, 2014 09:33AM EDT
-- None



Oct 20 (Reuters) - Valeant Pharmaceuticals Inc <VRX.TO> may raise its hostile takeover bid for Allergan Inc <AGN.N> and will not walk away from its pursuit ahead of Allergan's Dec. 18 special shareholder meeting, Chief Executive Michael Pearson said on Monday.

